Introduction

Hyun Ho is a South Korean rapper under Ai Grand Korea and a member of the boy group D-CRUNCH. He enlisted in the military on February 27, 2023, and was discharged on August 26, 2024. On February 3, 2023, he signed an exclusive contract with U Entertainment to pursue his dream as an actor.
